### ✅ Create a new session
POST http://localhost:3000/api/sessions
Authorization: Bearer <PASTE_JWT_HERE>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "therapistId": "665defabcdefabcdefabcdef",
  "patientId": "665abc123456789012345678",
  "type": "therapy",
  "scheduledAt": "2025-06-25T14:00:00Z"
}

### ✅ Get all sessions
GET http://localhost:3000/api/sessions
Authorization: Bearer <PASTE_JWT_HERE>

### ✅ Update session status
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/sessions/665session1234567890abcdef
Authorization: Bearer <PASTE_JWT_HERE>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "completed"
}